<node id="&quot;LIFE EXPECTANCY TRACKING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Life Expectancy Tracking is an ongoing measurement event documenting annual life expectancy at birth in Somalia over a 21-year period, showing fluctuations and an overall upward trend."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is an ongoing measurement event spanning from 2000 to 2021, documenting health and longevity trends."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is an ongoing measurement event spanning from 2000 to 2021, monitoring health outcomes in Equatorial Guinea."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is an ongoing measurement event spanning from 2000 to 2021, showing fluctuations in life expectancy at birth in Sudan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is an ongoing monitoring event spanning from 2000 to 2021, measuring life expectancy at birth in Madagascar."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is an ongoing monitoring event spanning from 2000 to 2021, measuring life expectancy at birth in years for Afghanistan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is the ongoing measurement and recording of life expectancy at birth in Bangladesh from 2000 to 2021, showing an overall increasing trend with a slight decline in 2020-2021."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is the ongoing measurement and recording of life expectancy at birth in Chad over a 21-year period from 2000 to 2021."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is the ongoing measurement and recording of life expectancy at birth in Iraq from 2000 to 2021."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is the ongoing measurement and recording of life expectancy at birth in Kuwait across multiple years from 2000 to 2021."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is the ongoing measurement and recording of life expectancy at birth in Paraguay across multiple years from 2000 to 2021."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is the ongoing measurement and recording of life expectancy at birth in Saint Lucia from 2000 to 2021, showing an overall increase from 73.22 years to a decline to 71.11 years in 2021."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Tracking is the ongoing measurement and recording of life expectancy at birth in Sweden from 2000 to 2021, showing a general upward trend with minor fluctuations."</data>
