  <data key="d1">"Year 2000 marks the beginning of life expectancy data collection for Papua New Guinea with a recorded value of 63.36 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of life expectancy data collection with a recorded value of 44.23425766 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection period for Egypt with a recorded value of 69.15 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection period for Tanzania with a recorded value of 52.79 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection period with a recorded value of 54.06 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection period with a recorded value of 71.07 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection period with a recorded value of 72.47 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection period with a recorded value of 78.17 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection with a recorded value of 71.4995438 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy data collection with a value of 65.65922366 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the starting point of life expectancy data collection for Eritrea with a value of 54.93 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the starting point of the life expectancy data collection for Azerbaijan with a value of 65.23 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2000 marks the starting point of the life expectancy data collection with a value of 78.11838329 years."</data>
