<node id="&quot;YEAR 2008&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Year 2008 is a data point in the life expectancy tracking for Egypt with a value of 69.77 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 48.29879732 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 58.75 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 60.44 years for Tanzania."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 64.35 years in Papua New Guinea."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 67.81121548 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 71.72 years for Georgia."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 73.71397618 years for Brazil."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 74.84 years for Algeria."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 records a life expectancy value of 80.29 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2008 represents a peak in life expectancy at 80.7993244 years before a decline in 2009."</data>
