<node id="&quot;YEAR 2020&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Year 2020 is a data point in the life expectancy tracking for Egypt with a value of 70.12 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 53.07817181 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 62.84 years, showing a decline from the previous year."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 66.27 years in Papua New Guinea, showing a decline from the previous year."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 67.40 years for Tanzania."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 72.14867013 years, showing a decline."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 73.11 years for Georgia."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 74.02 years for Algeria, showing a notable decline."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 74.11393563 years for Brazil, showing a decline."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 records a life expectancy value of 79.99 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 shows a notable decline in Azerbaijan's life expectancy to 71.43 years, likely due to external factors."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2020 shows a significant drop in life expectancy to 80.1312721 years, likely related to global events."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f66ee78a5eced5cb345f0e27d00f7203&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81b0111d393c89abb6529c89d28f71ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd5ab0c9f8976c21af87f61ad3906e22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4562f208582007473a0e4d2d73082fc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad4c147d13b05c581e7d456a1e775cb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ec678bc73a61287cf17cae4fd8b1425&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a515df61a1f38c587e87ee56973bb7cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f95bb6c38ce7e5ee8e3df6e5c964c23d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c5428da9ecad5d29f005287cf490438&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-459590cf6ff1db1a414d1f007654dbf3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bec15d0a142d47cc36b2c4a26fa1e017&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-35d1105fb767ca14efca2ea0425c7a63</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;YEAR 2021&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Year 2021 marks the end of the data collection period with a further decline to 78.30645695 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 marks the end of the data collection period with a recorded value of 78.63 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 marks the end of the life expectancy data collection period for Egypt with a recorded value of 69.11 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 marks the final year of recorded life expectancy data for Eritrea with a value of 63.57 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 52.30772755 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 63.40 years, the final year in the measurement series."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 65.49 years in Papua New Guinea, showing a further decline."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 66.81 years for Tanzania, showing a slight decline from 2020."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 69.55780877 years, showing a further decline."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 71.24 years for Georgia."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 72.38840694 years for Brazil, showing a significant decline."&lt;SEP&gt;"Year 2021 records a life expectancy value of 75.98 years for Algeria, showing recovery from 2020."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f66ee78a5eced5cb345f0e27d00f7203&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81b0111d393c89abb6529c89d28f71ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd5ab0c9f8976c21af87f61ad3906e22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad4c147d13b05c581e7d456a1e775cb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ec678bc73a61287cf17cae4fd8b1425&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a515df61a1f38c587e87ee56973bb7cc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f95bb6c38ce7e5ee8e3df6e5c964c23d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c5428da9ecad5d29f005287cf490438&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-459590cf6ff1db1a414d1f007654dbf3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bec15d0a142d47cc36b2c4a26fa1e017&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-35d1105fb767ca14efca2ea0425c7a63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d98017d05ca255da339820173c56ec99</data>
