  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Life Expectancy Trend 2000-2021 is a measured event documenting the progression of life expectancy at birth in Togo over a 22-year period, showing an increase from 56.08 to 63.86 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy Trend 2000-2021 is a measured phenomenon showing life expectancy at birth in Eswatini declining from 46.78 years in 2000 to a low of 41.78 years in 2005, then recovering to 54.59 years by 2021."</data>
