<edge source="&quot;WHOSIS_000001&quot;" target="&quot;LIFE EXPECTANCY MEASUREMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d3">208.0</data>
  <data key="d4">"WHOSIS_000001 conducts and maintains the Life Expectancy Measurement event, collecting annual data from 2000 to 2021."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is responsible for conducting and maintaining the Life Expectancy Measurement data collection."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is responsible for conducting and recording the Life Expectancy Measurement data."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is responsible for conducting and recording the Life Expectancy Measurement event."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is responsible for conducting and recording the Life Expectancy Measurement for Chile."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is responsible for recording and maintaining the Life Expectancy Measurement data."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is responsible for recording and reporting the Life Expectancy Measurement data."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the WHO statistical identifier associated with the Life Expectancy Measurement data."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the data source responsible for the Life Expectancy Measurement event."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the identifier for the Life Expectancy Measurement data series tracking annual values."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the organization responsible for conducting and recording Life Expectancy Measurement data."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the system or organization responsible for recording and maintaining the Life Expectancy Measurement data."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the system responsible for recording and maintaining Life Expectancy Measurement data across the 22-year period."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the system responsible for recording and maintaining the Life Expectancy Measurement data."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 is the system responsible for recording and reporting life expectancy measurements."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 records and maintains the Life Expectancy Measurement data across the 22-year period."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 records and tracks the Life Expectancy Measurement data for Malawi across multiple years."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 tracks and maintains the Life Expectancy Measurement data across the 22-year period."&lt;SEP&gt;"WHOSIS_000001 tracks and records life expectancy measurements as part of its health statistics database."</data>
  <data key="d5">chunk-d3735f27a2edc3d92886fdb8fd615f4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45249bd8ca7fe5789d8c3215ec997117&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5761911ea64906beea7cb7b9c96f464b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af069592a43e88b7821d49457cbf4d55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18c4209e18c6182e22c02fa694a7397e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4e6f5496a63d62bd10dd6397eb0dbf8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e05c79b12f9664c3496d0aa9d40fac14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-97b4a216982a88d1afcea6c1d9b2f3d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d2451968342ac15f0f23cd18f72fb65&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf9d1ab0f2377c85d00c1ec7effc2424&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-48849d265fa82b32624f9115355061d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ae5a70758eb7b864155c4ef35abd5208&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-34050c352e0462dddd367ebebf585b36&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4799890b0cf7018fe12cfbcb9c1f5a55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac0e050d04ccc91b40e67723d0f225ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f66ee78a5eced5cb345f0e27d00f7203&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc0f5a40bbb208dc293bbabce1e4777f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad4c147d13b05c581e7d456a1e775cb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d290066717f6a7f087fa19aed93dd5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b6bef4a932ef886528d1d647b15cd8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ae219b1bfad3d25ab0e0d067b51cb48&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4c1718b63d589f4dacf0d710702a789&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b978202e112f2d9f916f1d2fdb4e918</data>
  <data key="d6">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;WHOSIS_000001&quot;" target="&quot;LIFE EXPECTANCY AT BIRTH&quot;">
  <data key="d3">263.0</data>
  <data key="d4">WHOSIS_000001 is a dataset identifier and database system that collects, maintains, and tracks Life Expectancy at Birth as its primary health indicator metric. The dataset records annual Life Expectancy at Birth measurements across multiple countries, including Mozambique, Ecuador, and Zambia. Notably, WHOSIS_000001 documents a steady increase in Life Expectancy at Birth values over a 22-year period, rising from 59.09 years in 2000 to 66.10 years in 2021. As a key component of health information tracking systems, WHOSIS_000001 serves as the standardized identifier code for the Life Expectancy at Birth measurement series.</data>
  <data key="d5">chunk-f4ddbae1caf20a4e4dae93cea9b641e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3dc43161ed5e15900bdcdc3ff48ffe92&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e042ff49fa4eaf66944655e4118ff402&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26d04f81980e18ecd794d77a18c2d3c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4af5e466080dda642c52f93cb3f0647&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b1e24790db50459a1e34cc5efbd68eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-411f0104c2de30e00f13c543a160de71&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-533a481bb905ab470a19268d363eee4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32a69b081edd18c1f22aaabb0d4bf631&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf12e53e6780c19aac7babe1cab78a06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e0ca2d4499e0a10fe238b14c9b1cfc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd5ab0c9f8976c21af87f61ad3906e22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78c6b28bf541fb832a9469f6c0dda65c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5626994dc7cda440b4666693f91dfc11&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8f206ce1b3f4cb1cf03f9f3252a1233&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f31257e683f18222b592a30ce1ded771&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28d263258adfa460f065da8d0f8d6cb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0809df0acd3716ece554619bf8fe007d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0329eacee1863272a2d91eaff86fd5ae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98f4723c97a6e903f16b362615f9dc6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a28f514d6c71e276b356b0a0ff8b07b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9425f203ebebbf7c1f47dd38d5a73e9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b768704d04139b7047a187bf6b7ab90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b033e35ce042176b117951fd4aee6c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a42e2c68bd2247e770e5df2abb3aa774&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a600f289352b8248124278389f224a35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22eeffd503a1ae8891ad0de1746ff91f</data>
  <data key="d6">1</data>
</edge>
