  <data key="d4">"2020 shows an exceptional increase in Life Expectancy at Birth, rising to 77.26 years compared to previous years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy At Birth was recorded for New Zealand in 2020 with a value of 82.5016081 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy at Birth shows a notable decline in 2020 with a value of 69.33 years compared to previous years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy at Birth was measured in 2020 with a value of 66.18136667 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life expectancy experiences a sharp decline in 2020 to 75.19 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life expectancy was measured in 2020 with a value of 75.48 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"The year 2020 shows a notable decline in life expectancy to 77.56 years, a significant drop from 2019."&lt;SEP&gt;"The year 2020 shows a notable disruption in the upward trend of life expectancy, with a significant decline."</data>
  <data key="d5">chunk-0906334eef2f1fe26cee1854cf703614&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09c152a0f7bdda38da6384d4110e1ecf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e570c273d470373b477f73b6e4571b91&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d058c3e2db4946989da7a6173b3df5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28d263258adfa460f065da8d0f8d6cb9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-344900f08adfcdcec551beb06da47576&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-abb194cd22a1a18ea793da276d689f98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-664520362503a36836da4d0ba4aba116</data>
  <data key="d6">1</data>
</edge>
