  <data key="d3">82.0</data>
  <data key="d4">"2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy measurement period with an initial value of 65.16 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy At Birth was recorded for New Zealand in 2000 with a value of 78.57519182 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy at Birth measurement begins in 2000 with a value of 70.84 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy at Birth was measured in 2000 with a value of 59.08500401 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life Expectancy at Birth was measured in 2000 with a value of 64.07 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life expectancy measurement begins in 2000 with a value of 73.49 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life expectancy measurement recorded for FSM in 2000 with value 63.55831516 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Life expectancy was measured in 2000 with a value of 73.43 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"The year 2000 marks the beginning of life expectancy measurements with an initial value of 72.72 years."&lt;SEP&gt;"The year 2000 marks the beginning of the life expectancy measurement period with an initial value of 52.96 years."</data>
